('### BULO 2: "Ya sabemos la fecha exacta de inicio"  
A fecha de compilación de este manual **NO** se conoce la fecha exacta de apertura del plazo. Se sabe que será en **ABRIL de 2026**, pero no se sabe si será el 1, el 10 o el 15 de abril. Muchas personas en redes sociales afirman conocer la fecha exacta: **ES MENTIRA**. La fecha se conocerá con la publicación en el BOE.', '[-0.019755907,0.011084577,0.037304398,-0.06817159,0.009217894,0.025877418,0.013126117,-0.0025640896,-1.7097027e-05,0.021624705,-0.02949286,-9.085031e-06,0.007281122,0.015819335,0.13535435,0.011126356,0.003890063,0.012452712,-0.025523981,-0.020008428,0.009938236,0.0076757073,-0.00030200786,-0.011589991,-0.012384991,0.02027853,0.018371759,-0.00029397284,0.024825752,-0.010752058,-0.0014623493,-0.0034229404,0.008902702,0.029406656,-0.008198961,0.015754974,0.013597005,0.00784837,0.003253966,0.02226831,-0.0072071343,-0.007960123,-0.011607446,-0.02727336,0.008117617,-0.019454326,-0.025046606,-0.03128788,-0.0151783,0.021860052,-0.016300604,-0.0149124665,-0.028616415,-0.17314205,-0.022049753,-0.0018434359,-0.004451356,0.025527285,-0.002677835,-0.023853522,-0.037245966,0.031976607,-0.023885438,-0.0034283306,-0.008136672,-0.0014864211,-0.012281768,0.010273629,-0.010557146,-0.000934516,-0.012105096,-0.023534061,-0.0015246826,-0.011509426,-8.947537e-05,-0.014630574,-0.0062576775,0.013239792,-0.009906687,-0.002287621,-0.032107964,-0.018272419,-0.022946386,-0.009251611,-0.006992287,-0.007953702,0.013047914,-0.017787585,-0.01173505,-0.023100609,-0.021302182,0.028912693,-0.025897259,-0.02245894,0.003909945,-0.009409208,-0.00876469,-0.0056067333,-0.0142010115,-0.031849027,-0.009760926,-0.012109028,-0.019160653,-0.0076325024,0.031146811,-0.004785196,-0.012516822,0.0059197033,-0.0041932524,0.0019139008,-0.007022681,-0.0069496986,0.011802845,-0.0033440487,-0.0034335856,-0.16757789,0.0027747632,0.01374246,-0.009177365,-0.016766265,-0.0010564644,-0.016634265,-0.026291382,-0.010206402,-0.000487482,-0.0091848085,0.0051475693,-0.020104486,0.010353608,-0.0002185127,0.0104519