LA REGULARIZACI\u00d3N EXTRAORDINARIA", "subsection": "5. Documentaci\u00f3n necesaria", "subsubsection": "5.2.1. Problemas con la Apostilla de La Haya: plan de acci\u00f3n"}'),
('### 5.3. Acreditación de la estancia de 5 meses  
La forma principal de acreditar la estancia es el **padrón histórico**. Si tienes padrón, solícitalo lo antes posible, ya que las citas son difíciles de conseguir. **¡Empieza a pedir cita ya!** Para familias se necesita el **padrón de convivencia histórico**, aún más difícil de obtener.  
Si **no tienes padrón**, puedes acreditar la estancia con cualquier combinación de documentos alternativos: tarjetas de transporte, remesas, citas médicas, contratos de suministros, compras con tarjeta, documentación de entidades sociales, etc. (ver Sección 6 — El Cluedo Probatorio — para el listado completo).', '[-0.0016237508,0.015663385,0.024432166,-0.05316994,0.0073226234,0.0016385167,0.022673381,-0.003791595,0.015744926,0.006725637,-0.020094816,-0.0136748515,-0.020830782,0.021916127,0.11991523,0.012440697,-0.007818107,0.018272102,-0.00041164338,-0.015701769,0.022873593,0.0013146535,-0.023076147,-0.01634551,-0.011382944,0.011319368,0.021982221,0.019001015,0.03765934,-0.015376681,-0.0033455156,0.01767182,-0.021950899,0.018587245,-0.009856887,0.023807378,-0.0023348269,0.00060570793,0.0065910234,0.0056697354,-0.0029324556,-0.006576499,-0.005251632,-0.0069772163,0.013519437,-0.015186312,0.008513308,-0.0025795535,-0.014767518,0.004323949,0.012063396,-0.0059211585,-0.025402298,-0.17898059,-0.0017279543,-0.033998657,-0.014235894,0.017427767,-0.006369546,-0.020202639,-0.022466807,0.025537983,-0.004929005,0.004322278,0.023121672,0.011988845,0.013166722,0.030116025,0.005554266,-0.019179612,-0.019715998,0.012964339,0.010584018,-0.028938495,0.010013967,-0.030099194,-0.0042853192,0.007189029,-0.009770652,0.002818789,-0.000769995,-0.009623964,-0.0006508225,-0.0039762817,0.029684888,-0.010364954,0.0012650512,0.011198513,-0.012216823,0.014044233,0.0035649675,0.01896139,0.008118338,-0.020291386,0.029099813,-0.0055854428,-0.0018272375,-0.004544537,-0.020857148,-0.02239732,-0.0067854556,-0.021768168,-0.002834644,0.017192451,0.00985197,-0.03823515,-0.0046236226,0.014084249,0.00095924636,0.0073366873,0.010162091,-0.0046330313,-0.0070548737,0.023032682,0.0061176424,-0.17973836,-0.008136693,0.024346115,-0.0034559013,-0.027715402,-0.0071099913,0.007730743,-0.0008495265,-0.0023890196,0.010258337,-0.013200456,0.008981432,-0.0247944,-0.004836956,-0.019810623,-0.0043546427,-0.011416341,0.0