('### 12.2. Obtener el número de Seguridad Social  
**Posibles dificultades:**
En la práctica, para autentificarte telemáticamente necesitas la tarjeta vigente, lo que a veces genera "un laberinto" hasta que te dejan hacerlo con la cara del pasaporte. El movimiento está trabajando para facilitar estos mecanismos y preparar instrucciones claras (*"vale, tienes que decir tal, tal, tal, y a la tercera ya la tienes"*).', '[-0.015019199,0.005204012,0.0026416797,-0.05604064,0.0017560513,0.01233317,0.013161468,0.019374212,0.0076141935,0.003111316,-0.010484748,0.032685008,0.020339217,0.031249441,0.13964793,0.012645442,0.011663141,0.023645606,-0.012406681,-0.025261292,0.035031646,-0.0033345502,-0.029158214,-0.007503148,-0.001376739,-0.0013949608,0.024868356,0.011244218,0.047531795,-0.023378285,0.0064044516,0.015772065,0.009876529,0.041499276,-0.035469018,0.0072853006,0.011859514,-0.025578516,-0.011009973,0.010662601,0.029722614,-0.0004401688,0.0070457067,-0.014053966,0.018986812,-0.009797483,-0.0025682212,-0.01747278,0.00028519475,0.0036918153,0.0028796862,0.017649472,-0.040095784,-0.16568387,0.017504001,-0.03131108,0.0029708734,0.007038123,0.0023321388,-0.02536515,-0.031338103,0.017367547,-0.010489541,-0.0051929667,0.0028511027,-0.0009879537,0.032970402,0.029254392,-0.0004733505,-0.0191293,-0.011037286,-0.010042059,-0.013203944,-0.031603783,0.0031494906,-0.017452331,-0.011899671,0.012899863,-0.0017432639,-0.0021304074,-0.025843319,-0.0012105963,-0.005886966,0.0009373758,0.02098623,-0.022523949,0.021421693,0.01373741,-0.014821704,0.015213801,0.0064501567,0.018160831,0.0029082855,-0.022069503,0.021967795,-7.815192e-05,-0.01460532,0.015517085,0.0010316253,-0.0093909865,-0.014612345,-0.015499013,-0.0043496727,-0.0010699969,0.017268889,-0.036030468,-0.019057306,0.003986674,-0.00018229421,-0.0013564973,-0.0055767875,0.00077114004,-0.0033717512,0.01855277,0.007814976,-0.16581772,-0.0067103035,0.005846591,-0.012289569,-0.0061255293,0.017875014,0.009863408,0.007813156,0.010199135,0.0017000543,0.0005882635,0.016338296,-0.03079779,-0.0038554508,-0.002302337,0.01