('### 13.2. Ruta migratoria larga (tránsito por varios países)  
**Perfil:** Persona que ha pasado por múltiples países antes de llegar a España, sin haber residido legalmente en todos ellos.  
**Pregunta:** "He pasado por varios países en mi ruta migratoria, ¿necesito antecedentes de todos?"  
**Respuesta:** **NO.**  
**Explicación:** Solo se requieren antecedentes penales de los países donde se haya residido legalmente (con permiso de residencia, DNI, etc.). Los países de tránsito sin residencia legal no cuentan. Una persona con ruta migratoria larga no tiene que pedir antecedentes de todos los países de paso.', '[-0.001887172,0.014160462,0.021889405,-0.039009802,0.0012221569,0.025128538,0.025791585,0.008413643,0.014110354,-0.005826707,0.00702345,0.018276017,0.0034484938,0.0529652,0.11485368,0.025283383,0.010063511,0.016115738,-0.011246005,-0.00083977584,0.031975888,-0.0039689736,-0.024170628,0.0028787625,-0.022571202,0.01154733,0.015188458,0.0057200417,0.018359357,-0.022838343,0.0043057995,0.0039324025,0.0029263918,0.008811112,-0.021244878,0.02517695,-0.0042748773,-0.005896165,-0.009367711,-0.0015955371,0.0013794145,-0.010043016,-0.025048994,0.017077396,0.018441226,-0.029031888,0.011658035,0.015776016,-0.016360732,0.04334027,0.0028056619,0.0055154418,-0.03845479,-0.17283037,-0.020677397,-0.014091094,0.0055535487,-0.00386041,0.0054941433,-0.025149036,-0.0069285007,0.023101868,-0.011482862,-0.011469145,0.022556316,-0.0054381583,-0.007114263,0.034355793,-0.018995231,-0.013758798,-0.017302945,-0.008749474,-0.004410594,-0.017969027,0.01511041,-0.0077894027,0.0175173,0.015635291,-0.010856563,0.008647095,0.011258271,-0.0064608497,-0.005143776,0.0031139508,0.020451302,0.0015193179,0.0014501772,0.013023988,-0.0149621265,0.02854429,-0.0018444209,0.006420037,0.010875483,-0.020368291,0.02979321,-0.019212255,0.0031017466,0.015739055,-0.015296816,-0.03409904,-0.013359978,-0.012448771,0.0022198749,0.0068857027,0.02015214,-0.025329782,-0.015196795,0.01646884,0.011487731,-0.013016573,-0.002360022,-0.000379046,0.007274627,0.0198029,0.0146676125,-0.17469965,0.017180283,-0.0025384733,0.005554794,-0.005815384,-0.012549791,0.020989096,0.005963717,-0.0026716485,-0.0008973153,-0.01265478,0.010190549,-0.02444918,-0.01865402,-0.015050032,0.008926638,-0.007442955,0.004584864,-0.005948835,-0.0064505013,-0