('### 13.3. Llegada en patera  
**Perfil:** Persona que entró en España de forma irregular por vía marítima (patera u similar) antes del 31 de diciembre de 2025.  
**Pregunta:** "Si he venido en patera, ¿puedo acogerme a la regularización extraordinaria?"  
**Respuesta:** **SÍ.**  
**Explicación:** La forma de entrada en España no importa. Lo único necesario es acreditar haber entrado antes del 1 de enero de 2026. Puede hacerse con cualquier documento que sitúe a la persona en territorio español en esa fecha (ver Sección 6 — El Cluedo Probatorio — para el listado de pruebas válidas).', '[-0.007772092,0.016679168,0.032220572,-0.054455556,0.014960671,0.020460313,0.030144956,-0.0039136326,0.016533239,0.0031605323,-0.022129228,0.0022323194,-0.018260172,0.03427286,0.12924273,0.019073058,0.0033525361,0.017220635,-0.0033079167,-0.0054476187,0.049076542,0.012317793,-0.038329337,0.013464776,-0.016905362,0.017178046,0.03224681,-0.00028344893,0.029426582,-0.031213328,-0.02461691,0.0094845425,-0.027334802,0.026876053,-0.011178736,0.028293677,-0.00073000405,0.0078007807,0.0069201565,0.010266865,-0.0007295673,-0.022720179,-0.019099614,-0.006348303,0.023119988,-0.008251847,0.003029728,-0.017043127,-0.008232867,0.021352991,-0.014534399,-0.016978178,-0.03524076,-0.16949445,-0.012454801,-0.01314653,-0.006100687,0.00977472,-0.009992911,-0.015785027,-0.026902786,0.04222943,0.00047547036,-0.011676576,-3.7048245e-05,0.0108625,-0.0072532245,0.029708652,0.0023741492,-0.019958999,0.0044384208,-0.001890701,-0.006191885,-0.019453231,0.023446277,-0.013249056,-0.011832489,0.017347869,1.7406057e-05,0.002675588,-0.0041833045,-0.020608881,-0.00730767,-0.022424696,0.040438227,0.0021636148,0.0029561815,-0.0022098362,-0.016895777,0.009613697,-0.012234629,0.01539861,0.02988595,-0.020346016,0.0020921822,-0.008826828,-0.008982398,-0.010264881,0.0011117666,-0.026252488,-0.02249257,-0.01215121,0.0042739594,0.019937988,0.019448778,-0.024680935,0.006679968,0.022534424,0.007386909,0.012084264,-0.00063730945,-0.004219181,-0.0027096006,0.028348885,0.018140223,-0.17219618,0.016893735,0.008080916,0.016298635,0.0048850705,-0.01565748,0.0024399671,-0.028199943,0.012579283,-0.015122551,0.005774555,0.023333278,-0.04605234,0.010732578,-0.014162561,0.020482173,-0.0036197186,0.035951655,0.0006500