('### 13.14. Hijos menores de padres ya regularizados  
**Perfil:** Progenitor/a con residencia regular en España que tiene un/a hijo/a menor de edad en situación irregular.  
**Pregunta:** "Soy peruano, tengo residencia de trabajo por cuenta ajena y tengo una hija de 16 años. ¿Puedo regularizar a mi hija en esta regularización?"  
**Respuesta:** **SÍ.**  
**Explicación:** La regularización extraordinaria flexibiliza los requisitos para hijos/as de padres ya regularizados. A diferencia del reglamento ordinario (que exige 2 años de permanencia en España y condiciones económicas), con esta regularización no es necesario cumplir dichas condiciones.', '[0.004294276,0.019595198,0.02215439,-0.04729546,0.010019038,0.018731242,0.030067116,-0.006961279,0.015971154,-0.0076197246,0.0039129984,0.005302785,-0.0072646076,0.018811177,0.104546845,0.02964396,0.0016265039,0.025427701,-0.0032894989,-0.025285205,0.026368612,0.015937548,-0.037987318,0.0062378254,-0.03267405,0.026330724,0.011334634,0.00045853472,0.031811383,-0.020671884,-0.0045834417,0.011721176,-0.008136771,0.013420207,-0.044015173,0.028478574,-0.007916026,0.017455524,-0.017811079,-0.009555175,0.0031571966,0.0030229818,-0.02212135,-0.010264947,0.024625879,-0.014021788,-0.022823589,-0.024543121,-0.022970403,0.011410855,-0.009494376,-0.0076124542,-0.03861457,-0.16517232,-0.008543612,-0.0207415,-0.0061569246,-0.0057443967,-0.011318057,-0.015887126,-0.006146267,0.03233531,-0.008178624,-0.027093947,0.006097723,0.019450422,0.009160867,0.03362615,0.017746668,-0.03420747,0.010325352,-0.0034188505,-0.0021725115,-0.015858179,0.028144604,0.004548263,-0.0055661458,0.0046449862,-0.008079808,0.0038035156,-0.006103334,0.021188363,0.0021093965,-0.012209974,0.019655336,0.014249075,0.026537888,-0.0011058261,-0.010198212,0.0151229,-0.0015280872,0.015867716,0.0010400519,0.0023463261,0.0022325953,-0.003952165,0.010781597,0.013927481,-0.013323314,-0.026017018,-0.015283749,-0.0073334468,0.002065988,0.022301214,0.0054404926,-0.018466795,-0.003770663,0.013108492,-0.020847365,-0.004815909,0.005360709,-0.011131698,0.018570019,0.032946832,0.011095699,-0.16240652,0.0034552475,0.023243245,-0.0066079353,-0.008419412,0.0009430022,0.018951617,-0.011642453,0.020709138,-0.012515661,-0.0070080142,0.025196293,-0.03143723,-0.016338564,-0.02245357,-0.0013360142,0.008191708,0.0077193636,0.0056537907,-0.00500477