| **2020** | El movimiento Regularización Ya impulsa una **Proposición No de Ley** en el Congreso de los Diputados. Fue rechazada por los mismos partidos que hoy "se cuelgan la medalla" de haber sacado la regularización. En aquel momento, estos partidos argumentaron que el Pacto Europeo de Migración y Asilo no lo permitía. **ERA MENTIRA.** El movimiento lo sabía y siguió insistiendo. |', '[-0.00013362634,0.02236742,0.027923224,-0.06269723,0.0010043978,0.023811117,0.014430197,-0.017304294,-0.011084619,0.0068830145,-0.009053665,0.010241551,0.0059863585,0.034795325,0.110289834,0.025675973,0.0021486424,0.017090775,-0.016083715,0.0026917818,0.035676774,-0.00916264,-0.008015325,-0.0029436927,-0.017848745,0.008472337,0.025885155,0.013506001,0.030171411,-0.006983059,0.016912367,0.005542569,0.010476627,0.012800824,-0.01445588,0.014737928,-0.0019670976,0.010884053,-0.003948388,0.035287544,-0.009009374,-0.0016817147,-0.007853288,-0.004990805,0.013492142,-0.0007088316,-0.014918387,-0.032261007,-0.0050428356,-0.0043311953,-0.013137142,-0.015405309,-0.0076618935,-0.15840116,-0.008124707,-0.002800492,-0.0057161273,0.011217193,0.02894244,-0.015334078,-0.008494904,0.00793144,-0.010168149,-0.031492252,-0.00396838,-0.00024990152,0.014319641,0.025884217,0.0011358815,-0.014121609,-0.0011669124,-0.010209042,-0.0005849358,-0.010243984,0.0061202985,-0.008539722,0.016688926,0.026681641,0.012655192,0.0025579648,-0.021144565,0.008080492,0.0035801316,-0.0016217466,0.016267028,0.015532253,0.025381604,-0.021267964,-0.00737037,0.012337639,-0.011089911,0.036219068,-0.018628644,-0.03378419,0.0057134377,-0.006148284,0.0038524005,0.0058219437,-0.0139895305,-0.021551734,-0.009193496,-0.017920269,-0.007954009,0.007411856,0.035954062,0.00092462084,-0.012355316,0.020823998,0.0031803914,-0.0033736925,0.0034833567,-0.004554051,-0.002941508,0.01403065,0.005105992,-0.19125299,0.01027642,0.008029218,0.004877736,-0.012998412,-0.009328827,0.029439067,-0.0060237255,0.022031752,0.011606706,-0.020202834,-0.0005531