('| **2023** | Los partidos que habían dicho apoyar la ILP se olvidaron durante las elecciones; en ninguna plataforma electoral aparecía el apoyo a la ILP. Estos mismos partidos votaron calladamente el traspaso de competencias propuesto por Junts per Catalunya, que definía a las personas migrantes como "peligro para la sociedad" y se sumaba al discurso de la deportación. El movimiento presionó a Podemos para que bloqueara un acuerdo de traspaso de competencias que, en la práctica, significaba traspasar delegaciones para deportar y gestionar CIE (Centros de Internamiento de Extranjeros). |', '[0.009273692,0.014893342,0.036021203,-0.046052903,0.0105984835,0.014386897,0.015941873,0.011225972,0.0066366885,-0.0051963185,-0.017189912,-0.007713851,0.011181095,0.017284578,0.12374255,0.01561487,-0.01049957,0.025352806,-0.015271697,0.004473804,0.04056331,-0.01815585,-0.009503822,0.0068988265,-0.02854488,0.012109185,0.021955954,0.01888649,0.008416182,-0.015458294,0.015763002,0.0049875113,-0.0012060269,-0.0006268587,-0.017371016,0.017972294,0.0064095156,0.011174669,0.014985281,0.021772245,-0.002396687,0.0028807616,-0.010355281,0.00030955218,0.013111527,-0.01915531,-0.0072295777,-0.020292303,-0.022948045,-0.030465936,0.0037556423,0.0104154255,-0.0154088,-0.14970112,-0.0019190086,-0.010725068,0.00815326,0.0005470161,0.001394987,-0.016341778,-0.006569165,-0.0026438541,-0.003995026,-0.018160634,0.026663298,-0.011963836,0.00056957005,0.032596678,0.0034225897,0.0026668094,0.00855699,-0.008935883,0.01419192,-0.008767052,0.00036400085,-0.009176316,0.02021883,0.008418537,0.009125529,0.008648921,-0.016285744,0.0049618436,0.0051269988,-0.019996442,0.012755162,0.0004293283,-0.008023873,-0.020199366,0.013345386,0.0013503603,-0.006848659,0.014720476,-0.002949921,-0.015909446,-0.0047099716,0.0010627486,0.008521981,0.012268903,-0.01903233,-0.01845643,-0.022707956,-0.005655332,0.010255047,0.007940365,0.0029624898,-0.025852138,-0.022081474,0.015067785,-0.022972269,-0.017985126,-0.0031157576,-0.0